@startuml
title User Interaction Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "Expo App" as App
participant "Firebase Authentication" as Auth
participant "Firestore" as DB
participant "Firebase Storage" as Storage
participant "GPS Service" as GPS
participant "Firebase Cloud Messaging" as FCM
participant "Emergency Contacts" as Contacts

User -> App : Launch app
activate App
App -> Auth : Authenticate user
activate Auth
Auth --> App : Login success
deactivate Auth
deactivate App

== View Disaster Reports ==
User -> App : View reports
activate App
App -> DB : Fetch reports
activate DB
DB --> App : Report list
deactivate DB
App --> User : Display list / map
deactivate App

== Create Disaster Report ==
User -> App : Create report
activate App
App -> GPS : Fetch location
activate GPS
GPS --> App : Coordinates
deactivate GPS
User -> App : Add details & media
App -> Storage : Upload media
activate Storage
Storage --> App : Media URL
deactivate Storage
App -> DB : Save report
activate DB
deactivate DB
deactivate App

== Vote on Report ==
User -> App : Confirm / Dismiss report
activate App
App -> DB : Save vote
activate DB
DB --> App : Vote recorded
deactivate DB
deactivate App

== Manage Emergency Contacts ==
User -> App : Add / Update contacts
activate App
App -> DB : Save contacts
activate DB
DB --> App : Confirmation
deactivate DB
deactivate App

== SOS Emergency ==
User -> App : Press SOS
activate App
App -> DB : Check saved contacts
activate DB
DB --> App : Contact list
deactivate DB
App -> GPS : Get live location
activate GPS
GPS --> App : Coordinates
deactivate GPS
App -> Contacts : Send SOS alert
activate Contacts
App -> DB : Store SOS event
activate DB
deactivate DB
deactivate Contacts
deactivate App

== Notifications ==
FCM --> App : Receive notification
activate App
App --> User : Show alert
deactivate App

@enduml
